saveTaskList() - Method in class wei.task.Controller
Save changes of all the current tasks into the file: "taskList.bin" with a binary format, it can be loaded next time when initialize the Controller.
SaveTaskListToFile(String) - Method in class wei.task.TaskManager
The SaveTaskListToFile method will write the task list to the file with binary format, it can be loaded by the TaskManager.loadTaskListFromFile(String) method.

setTaskName(String) - Method in class wei.task.Task

showTaskByTime() - Method in class wei.task.Controller
The showTaskByTime will show all the tasks with the sorting order of create time.
size() - Method in class wei.task.TaskManager
Return the size of the current task list.
sortByTime() - Method in class wei.task.TaskManager
The sortByTime method will sort all the tasks by the task's create time in a ascending order.
